# Exercise 000 - Installing Docker - Solutions

1) apt-get -y install docker-ce # Debian/Ubuntu

OR

yum -y install docker # Red Hat / CentOS 

2) adduser <youruser> docker

3) docker ps
CONTAINER ID        IMAGE               COMMAND                  CREATED             STATUS              PORTS                    NAMES

4) Be sure "source /etc/profile.d/bash_completion.sh" is somewhere in your local .bashrc file
